# Title: HackTool - SharpEvtMute Execution
# Author: Florian Roth (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2022-09-07
# Level: high
# Description: Detects the use of SharpEvtHook, a tool that tampers with the Windows event logs
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1685.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_hktl_sharpevtmute.yml

Image="*\\SharpEvtMute.exe" OR Description="SharpEvtMute" OR CommandLine IN ("*--Filter \"rule *", "*--Encoded --Filter \\\"*")